documents.content: Name: Bhuvan Subramani. Title: Bhuvan Subramani - Data Science & Software Engineering Portfolio. Project: HyperScale Retail Command Center. Category: data, ml-ai. Description: Implemented an end-to-end Real-Time Analytics solution on Microsoft Fabric. The project unifies historical sales data and real-time order streams into a Medallion Architecture, utilizing PySpark for ETL and Facebook Prophet for accurate 30-day demand forecasting. It closes the loop with Fabric Activator to deliver stockout alerts in under one minute, turning passive data into proactive, actionable business intelligence.. Technologies used: Microsoft Fabric, PySpark, Facebook Prophet, Real-Time Streaming, Power BI, Delta Lake, Data Engineering, Time-Series ML. Key Metrics: Alert Latency < 1 Minute, 30 Day Demand Forecast, 100% Automated Pipeline. Link: https://bhuvanps.github.io/Portfolio/Hyperscale/.

Project: Bank Loan Performance Analysis. Category: data. Description: Designed a three-tier Power BI dashboard monitoring $435.8M in loans. Implemented complex DAX measures for MTD/MoM tracking. Achieved 86.2% Good Loan rate with data-driven insights on risk exposure and debt consolidation strategy.. Technologies used: Power BI, DAX, Financial Analysis, KPIs. Key Metrics: $435.8M Portfolio, 86.2% Success Rate. Link: https://bhuvanps.github.io/Portfolio/Loan_Analysis_Report/.
